	<Description>
		This site includes a complete set of workbooks designed for use in small group Torah studies.
		The material is at a beginning to intermediate level and is well-suited to those who have a strong desire to know more about our God through the study of His Torah.
		It only requires a willing leader and motivated participants to have a life-changing encounter with the God of Abraham, Isaac and Jacob.
	</Description>
